Selected Publications


Johnson, S. C., Wicks, M., Žefran, M., and DeCarlo, R. A. (2018). The structured distance to the nearest system without property P. IEEE Transactions on Automatic Control, 63(9), 2960–2975. https://doi.org/10.1109/TAC.2018.2817163
Noohi, E., Žefran, M., and Patton, J. L. (2016). A model for human–human collaborative object manipulation and its application to human–robot interaction. IEEE Transactions on Robotics, 32(4), 880–896. https://doi.org/10.1109/TRO.2016.2572698
Parastegari, S., Noohi, E., Abbasi, B., and Žefran, M. (2018). Failure recovery in robot-human object handover. IEEE Transactions on Robotics, 34(3), 660–673. https://doi.org/10.1109/TRO.2018.2819198
Abbasi, B., Monaikul, N., Rysbek, Z., Di Eugenio, B., & Žefran, M. (2019). A Multimodal Human-Robot Interaction Manager for Assistive Robots. 2019 IEEE/RSJ International Conference on Intelligent Robots and Systems (IROS), 6756–6762. https://doi.org/10.1109/IROS40897.2019.8968505
Monaikul, N., Abbasi, B., Rysbek, Z., Di Eugenio, B., & Žefran, M. (2020). Role Switching in Task-Oriented Multimodal Human-Robot Collaboration. 2020 29th IEEE International Conference on Robot and Human Interactive Communication (RO-MAN), 1150–1156. https://doi.org/10.1109/RO-MAN47096.2020.9223461




